These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, comedy, fantasy, mystery
4 different pets are kept: bird, hedgehog, lizard, rat
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, february, june, september
City: nizza, rome, london, san-francisco
1. the person who's birthday is in february is the owner of the rat##1
2. the person who's birthday is in june is between the person watching fantasy movies and the person watching mystery movies##2
3. the person who's birthday is in february is the person traveling to nizza##1
4. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
5. the owner of the bird is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
6. the person traveling to london is the person watching fantasy movies##1
7. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
8. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far right##1
9. the person watching comedy movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy | mystery   | adventure  | fantasy  |
| Pet   | hedgehog    | rat    | bird      | lizard    |
| Birthday   | september | february | june | december |
| City     | san-francisco  | nizza       | rome    | london     |

