.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, june, march, december
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, adventure, scientific, western
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, zinnia, begonia, iris
House: modern, cottage, craftsman, townhouse
1. the townhouse house is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
2. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far right##1
3. the person who growsiris is the cottage house##1
4. the person who's birthday is in march is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
5. the person watching western movies is between the person who growsbegonia and the modern house##2
6. the townhouse house is between the person watching western movies and the person who growsiris##2
7. the person who growsmarigold is on the far right##1
8. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
9. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the person who growszinnia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Birthday         | december | june    | march  | april    |
| Movie-Genre   | action      | adventure  | western  | scientific |
| Flower           | iris      | begonia       | zinnia      | marigold       |
| House         | cottage    | townhouse | craftsman | modern |

