.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
There are 4 different nationalities: spanish, british, egyptian, japanese
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, begonia, bellflower, azalea
4 different games are played: whist, backgammon, poker, bridge
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, motorbike, roller, subway
1. the person playing poker is the person driving the motorbike##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
3. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
5. the egyptian is on the left of the person who growsbellflower##1
6. the person playing backgammon is the person who growsazalea##1
7. the japanese is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
8. the spanish is between the person who growstulip and the person who growsazalea##2
9. the person who growsbellflower is between the egyptian and the person playing backgammon##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Nationality        | british | egyptian     | spanish   | japanese     |
| Flower       | begonia   | tulip   | bellflower | azalea |
| Game         | whist   | poker | bridge       | backgammon    |
| Transport   | roller    | motorbike | helicopter  | subway    |

