.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-4::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, jet-ski, quad-bike, roller
City: colone, boston, rome, liverpool
4 different pets are kept: bird, frog, hamster, pony
There are 4 different favourite colors: ivory, azure, yellow, aquamarine
 1. the person traveling to boston is on the far right##1
 2. the person traveling to liverpool is the person driving the bike##1
 3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person who likes aquamarine##1
 4. the person who likes ivory is on the far left##1
 5. the person traveling to liverpool is the owner of the frog##1
 6. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person who likes ivory##1
 7. the person traveling to boston is the person driving the quad-bike##1
 8. the person traveling to colone is on the right of the person traveling to liverpool##1
 9. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person who likes azure##1
10. the person driving the jet-ski is between the owner of the bird and the person driving the roller##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Transport           | bike  | roller | jet-ski     | quad-bike |
| City   | liverpool | colone  | rome | boston       |
| Pet           | frog       | pony    | hamster      | bird           |
| Color         | ivory | azure   | aquamarine   | yellow         |

