.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-5::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, bike, snowmobile, subway
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: aristoff, oliveros, game, fonseca
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, epic, romance, scientific
4 different pets are kept: ferret, snake, cat, horse
 1. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
 2. the owner of the ferret is on the far left##1
 3. the game-smoker is the person driving the bike##1
 4. the game-smoker is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 5. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person driving the subway##1
 6. the person driving the snowmobile is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
 7. the fonseca-smoker is on the left of the person driving the ship##1
 8. the oliveros-smoker is the person watching epic movies##1
 9. the person driving the snowmobile is between the owner of the horse and the person watching adventure movies##2
10. the person watching romance movies is the owner of the cat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
| Transport          | bike         | snowmobile         | ship     | subway      |
| Cigar           | game | fonseca | aristoff    | oliveros     |
| Movie-Genre   | adventure      | romance       | scientific    | epic       |
| Pet         | ferret     | cat       | horse | snake |

