.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-6::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, hiking, baking, reading
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, skateboard, boat, car
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, dutch, polish, turkish
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, april, february, january
1. the person driving the taxi is between the person who's birthday is in january and the person driving the boat##2
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is between the person driving the taxi and the turkish##2
3. the polish is between the person who's birthday is in april and the dutch##2
4. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left of the dutch##1
5. the polish is the polish##1
6. the dutch is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
7. the dutch is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
8. the person driving the boat is on the far right##1
9. the person driving the skateboard is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Hobby           | baking | hiking | video-games  | reading |
| Transport   | skateboard      | car       | taxi     | boat      |
| Nationality   | turkish   | dutch      | polish   | chinese   |
| Birthday         | february   | january    | march | april   |

