 7. the cape-cod house is the davidoff-smoker##1
 8. the fan of soul is on the far right##1
 9. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
10. the art-deco house is the bongani-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Beverage   | juice | soy-milk | 7up  | mirinda  |
