 6. the person who growsaconite is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 8. the person who growsmarigold is on the far right##1
 9. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the person who's hobby is reading and the person watching adventure movies##2
10. the person eating tomato is on the left of the person eating spinach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | tomato        | spinach    | grapefruit | lettuce   |
