 8. the person who's sport is swimming is between the french and the australian##2
 9. the spanish is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
10. the person playing bridge is between the french and the australian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4       |
